Module mesakit.data.formats.pbf
Package com.telenav.mesakit.map.data.formats.pbf.processing

Interface PbfDataSource

All Superinterfaces:
com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Broadcaster, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.messaging.Receiver, com.telenav.kivakit.resource.Resourceful, com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Transceiver, com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.messaging.Transmitter
All Known Implementing Classes:
BasePbfReader, ParallelPbfReader, SerialPbfReader
public interface PbfDataSource extends com.telenav.kivakit.resource.Resourceful, com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.Broadcaster
A source of PBF data which can be processed by an PbfDataProcessor. The method process(PbfDataProcessor) pushes data to the data processor object, which processes the ways, nodes and relations in receives. The number of ways, nodes and relations in the data source can be retrieved with ways(), nodes() and relations(), respectively. Metadata from the PBF file can be accessed with metadata(). The methods onStart() are called onEnd() are called before and after processing.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
